sigma_analysis_results.rule_title: New DLL Added to AppInit_DLLs Registry Key
sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: DLLs that are specified in the AppInit_DLLs value in the Registry key HKLM\Software\Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion\Windows are loaded by user32.dll into every process that loads user32.dll
